00:10:06.700 --> 00:10:07.540
He Datian.

00:10:08.600 --> 00:10:10.340
How could you act in such a way?

00:10:10.620 --> 00:10:12.240
Strike their names from the clan registry.

00:10:12.700 --> 00:10:13.780
Village Chief,

00:10:13.780 --> 00:10:15.300
we swear we'll never do it again.

00:10:15.780 --> 00:10:17.260
For the sake of all the times,

00:10:17.260 --> 00:10:18.620
I've shown you respect...

00:10:18.940 --> 00:10:19.780
Enough.

00:10:21.020 --> 00:10:23.220
You didn't cause any grave trouble.

00:10:24.100 --> 00:10:24.980
You'll just pay

00:10:24.980 --> 00:10:26.700
to get the village's archway repaired.

00:10:27.220 --> 00:10:28.060
Village Chief.

00:10:28.820 --> 00:10:30.820
You're letting them off so lightly?

00:10:35.020 --> 00:10:36.260
What's wrong, my dear?

00:10:36.260 --> 00:10:37.380
Village Chief, my wife...

00:10:37.380 --> 00:10:38.700
Quick, fetch a physician.

00:10:39.340 --> 00:10:40.420
Hurry!

00:10:41.740 --> 00:10:42.960
Xifeng, let's get a physician.

00:10:56.060 --> 00:10:57.380
Sorry, I came too late.

00:10:58.700 --> 00:10:59.820
You've suffered so much.

00:11:01.730 --> 00:11:02.700
It's not your fault.

00:11:03.500 --> 00:11:05.960
It was my own idea from the start.

00:11:12.220 --> 00:11:13.100
Are you alright?

00:11:18.620 --> 00:11:19.700
It will be fine.

00:11:29.300 --> 00:11:30.140
Oh, right.

00:11:31.450 --> 00:11:33.850
You could sneak into He Datian's home

00:11:35.460 --> 00:11:37.180
and without anyone noticing,

00:11:37.180 --> 00:11:38.740
you tampered with the final letter.

00:11:40.660 --> 00:11:41.980
How did you pull that off?

00:11:45.540 --> 00:11:47.100
Thanks to the days in the bandit den,

00:11:47.220 --> 00:11:48.540
I picked up some combat skills.

00:11:51.060 --> 00:11:52.300
(Why would the bandits)

00:11:52.300 --> 00:11:54.580
(teach a scholar martial arts?)

00:11:55.140 --> 00:11:56.620
(And if he mastered such skills,)

00:11:57.140 --> 00:11:58.620
(how could he have been trapped there)

00:11:58.620 --> 00:11:59.500
(all these years?)

00:12:00.260 --> 00:12:01.140
Fu Qinghuai,

00:12:04.540 --> 00:12:05.900
who are you, truly?

